---
import face from '~/assets/images/home-computer.webp';
---

<div class="relative flex-1 flex flex-col px-5 sm:px-12 pb-11 min-h-0">
  <img
    src={face.src}
    width={480}
    height={480}
    alt=""
    loading="lazy"
    class="absolute left-1/2 top-1/2 -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 opacity-[0.16] pointer-events-none"
  />
  <div class="relative flex-1 flex flex-col justify-center items-center gap-[22px] min-h-0 text-center">
    <div class="overflow-hidden w-full">
      <h1
        class="display-text leading-none moveup-text text-center"
        style="font-size: clamp(64px, 9vw, 140px); letter-spacing: 0.1em"
      >
        About
      </h1>
    </div>
    <div class="eyebrow">I'm John. A senior full-stack engineer building agentic systems and production web apps.</div>
    <p class="text-[15px] leading-[1.65] max-w-[620px] m-0" style="color: var(--text-body)">
      I build LLM-driven tools, modern front ends, and the glue between them: LangGraph workflows, constrained action
      spaces, typed state surfaces, eval infrastructure, and production Angular/React applications.
    </p>
    <p class="text-[15px] leading-[1.65] max-w-[620px] m-0" style="color: var(--text-body)">
      Most recently at Rohirrim AI, I built a LangGraph-based test-failure triage agent, delivered most of a NextGen
      frontend prototype, migrated document processing from NestJS to FastAPI with Docling, and owned Angular framework
      upgrades through v20.
    </p>
    <div class="flex flex-col gap-1.5 items-center">
      <div class="eyebrow-sm">Skills</div>
      <div class="text-sm leading-[1.6] max-w-[620px]" style="color: var(--text-body)">
        LLM Agents / LangGraph / TypeScript / Angular 4–20 / React / Python / FastAPI / Node.js / NgRx SignalStore /
        TanStack Query / RxJS / Playwright / Docker / AWS / REST APIs /
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-4 justify-center mt-2">
      <a class="fancy-button" href="/files/John_Fewell-Resume.pdf" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer"> Resume </a>
      <a class="fancy-button" href="mailto:fewell@gmail.com"> Contact </a>
    </div>
  </div>
</div>
